      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require significant mechanical work to become roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows substantial rust, several large dents, and peeling clear coat, while the interior has significant wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer, as the car cannot be driven in its current state. Despite these challenges, it could serve as a valuable donor car for a restoration project.",
